\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces  SPR chain simulation with missing data. On the left panel we see the MDS projections of the samples when their signal is calculated from similar reference trees, and on the right we have the projections when random species trees are used. The colors represent the four groupings (consecutive trees in the SPR chain, separated from each other by more SPR branch swappings) defined in the simulation. }}{10}{figure.caption.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{figure002}{{2}{10}{SPR chain simulation with missing data. On the left panel we see the MDS projections of the samples when their signal is calculated from similar reference trees, and on the right we have the projections when random species trees are used. The colors represent the four groupings (consecutive trees in the SPR chain, separated from each other by more SPR branch swappings) defined in the simulation}{figure.caption.2}{}}
